{"tid":691332,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"係邊個買撚晒波仔咖哩雞球飯？","createTime":"2018-06-05T15:35:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-06T14:32:22.000Z","uid":2104,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"115aced67af84031399997c3be1c3cbd5257a605","tid":691332,"uid":2104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T15:35:23.000Z","msg":"兩日喇...<br />\n琴日收工餓餓地諗住去些粉買我最愛嘅波仔咖哩雞球飯 點知去到搵 竟然冇晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n平時點都會有兩三盒<br />\n跟住行過兩條街間些粉 又冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係個魚香茄子同梅菜扣肉就仍然健在<br />\n再行遠少少 又係冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n算！我放棄 唯有餓一晚<br />\n好啦<br />\n今日我落些粉搵 又係冇 <br />\n屌你究竟邊撚個買晒我啲波仔咖哩雞球飯？"},{"pid":"ac80c13719fd4dc87244f17bcda194b498369ab2","tid":691332,"uid":27251,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T15:38:24.000Z","msg":"波仔係唔係執晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1a528175c4005c18fac503f97e563dc998ed2da","tid":691332,"uid":2104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ac80c13719fd4dc87244f17bcda194b498369ab2","tid":691332,"uid":27251,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T15:38:24.000Z","msg":"波仔係唔係執晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T15:39:40.000Z","msg":"唔好呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我想食咖哩雞球飯呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8247310d4bd6fabfb6550ec2dc0ef73ef8a92c57","tid":691332,"uid":61607,"like":25,"dislike":1,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T15:41:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ae637899bda249f0fb0acd8752c724766b7257e6","tid":691332,"uid":75754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T15:48:04.000Z","msg":"咖哩牛肉咪仲好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91d26f00335fdb26752e1c1